race.name: Bass Pro Shops NRA Night Race
race.comments: Kyle Busch won the UNOH 200 at Bristol Motor Speedway, his 49th victory in the NASCAR Camping World Truck Series. Prior to the start of the race, the following cars dropped to the rear of the field for the reasons indicated: No.1 (engine change) and No. 52 (missing driver crew chief meeting).
